      <akn:section eId="sec_44_110_03">
        <akn:num>44-110.03</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>General building exterior.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-110_03_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>An ALR shall ensure that the exterior of its facility, including walkways, yards, porches, chimney, gutters, downspouts, paintable surfaces, and accessory buildings are maintained structurally sound, sanitary, and in good repair.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-110_03_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>An ALR that provides services to residents who use wheelchairs, shall make reasonable accommodations to render the ALR accessible to residents who use wheelchairs through the installation of a chair lift, curbcuts, an exterior ramp, or like accommodations.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
